---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn more about StarterForge and the team behind it.">
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        About StarterForge
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        <p>
          StarterForge was born out of frustration. Every time we started a new SaaS project,
          we spent days -- sometimes weeks -- setting up the same foundational pieces: dark mode,
          responsive navigation, blog infrastructure, SEO meta tags, and deployment configuration.
        </p>
        <p>
          We built StarterForge to eliminate that repetitive setup work. It is a carefully crafted
          Astro 5 starter kit that includes everything you need to launch a professional SaaS
          landing page, complete with Tailwind CSS v4 styling, a blog powered by MDX content
          collections, and production-ready SEO configuration.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our goal is simple: help developers ship faster. Instead of spending your first sprint
          on boilerplate, you can focus on what makes your product unique from day one.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Team section -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Our Team</h2>
        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-400 to-primary-600"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Alex Turner</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Creator & Lead Developer</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="h-16 w-16 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-teal-600"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Jordan Lee</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Design & UX</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
